<p>We can customise the message of an assertion like this:</p>  <pre><code>$this-&gt;assertEquals(true, false, 'should be equal'); </code></pre>  <p>I have a mock object:</p>  <pre><code>$mockExecutionContext = $this-&gt;getMock('some interface'); $mockExecutionContext-&gt;expects($this-&gt;once())-&gt;method('someMethod'); </code></pre>  <p>How can I customise the message displayed when this gets verified?</p>